RE: i need Anxiety help :( It is difficult to say how to cure your problem without knowing the cause. I had suffered from it as well, until I just said fuck it, the world is screwed up and I will be who I want to be. No apologies and no guilt. I no longer care at all what others think. You need to identify exactly what is causing those feelings and talk to someone about that. I believe medications can do many things, howver cure anxiety and many other mental problems no. The best it can do is hide the symptoms.
