RE: i need Anxiety help :( Very gently dissecting what is actually worrying you might help.
As for public speaking; if sweating and palpitations take place, there is an exercise known as paradoxical intention. You will your heart to beat faster, and to sweat more profusely, and the body tends to do the opposite.
This method was devised by a psychiatrist (forget his name) while in a concentration camp.
